replies.body:
I filed a support ticket and the great MouseRat let me know my graphics card driver was out of date. I had previously checked settings via the control panel and (attempted to) manually updated the drivers, and Windows/NVidia said they were up to date. However, something in there had become corrupt and resulted in my driver thinking it was updated although it was not. 

A clean reset and update on the graphics card totally fixed everything! Support answered my ticket in 7 minutes. Thanks again :)

